          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1611311279106-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>green tomato chutney</strong> with the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]<strong> </span>lemon</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>green tomato dressing</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
